{
  "stem": "14463.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, so we went back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From Kyzylorda we went back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There's one thing I want to tell you what happened on the way, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One little thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Two things, actually, to give you some idea what was going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "First of all, there was a trainload of 500 people again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Somehow we always had trainloads of 500 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So many wagons and so many people in wagons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So again, everybody was on lying on the floor, on a bit of straw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was, you know, I was always, you know, thinking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they said, in Poland, there's a lake of salt-- salt is like gold, and also rice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went-- in Kyzylorda was plenty of rice, and we bought some rice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the Caspian Sea, when we were passing the Caspian sea, we bought salt, because that's where the salt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I had two big bags, one rice, and one salt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A few schmattas.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Really, a few schmattas.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on the way, we were going to west Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, the trains with troops were coming back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One more thing I forgot to tell you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Kyzylorda I met, you know, when I was on the railway station, there was a passenger train, and out came German officers, and [INAUDIBLE] Paulus was there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I saw [INAUDIBLE] Paulus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, that was the defender, the marshal, which was fighting for Stalingrad, right?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, so, and trainloads of German troops which were coming back, you know, and they were chucking out the dead on the line, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, going back to Poland, on the way there was such misery that you have never seen in your life.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because a lot of people came out from concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
